data.title: Musicas Japonesas
data.meta_description: musicas_japonesas - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document appears to be a listing of Japanese musical artists along with song titles and codes. There are over 200 entries listed with the artist's name, song code, and Japanese song title. The listing includes a variety of popular Japanese artists from different decades ranging from the 1970s to present day.
